OL,3,CBillionaire Guernsey golf investor
OL,4,Cwants to inspire tourism boost
OL,6,FA billionaire Guernsey businessman
OL,7,Fhopes more people will invest in the
OL,8,Fisland to increase its attractiveness
OL,9,Fto tourists.
OL,11,FSteve Lansdown has spent millions on
OL,12,Fthe La Grande Mare Country Club and
OL,13,FGolf Resort on the west coast and
OL,14,Fwould like to see other investors
OL,15,Ffollow suit to make the most of the
OL,16,Fopportunities the island has to offer.
OL,18,FHe says: "If this develops as I think
OL,19,Fit will, I think other people will
OL,20,Finvest in the infrastructure.
