OL,3,CBillionaire Guernsey golf investor
OL,4,Cwants to inspire tourism boost
OL,6,F"Guernsey needs to raise its bar, talk
OL,7,Fitself up - not in a boastful fashion
OL,8,F- but encourage people to come to the
OL,9,Fisland."
OL,11,FMr Lansdown adds: "I talk to my
OL,12,Ffriends from the UK or around the
OL,13,Fworld and they talk about the
OL,14,FOccupation, the history and the beauty
OL,15,F- they are astounded and they want to
OL,16,Fcome. This will be one of the reasons
OL,17,Fto come."
OL,19,FThe media were invited to a preview
OL,20,Fthe new Golf Performance Centre, which
OL,21,Fis soon opening to the public.
