OL,6,FIt is considered the first major
OL,7,Fmilestone in La Grande Mare's phased
OL,8,Fdevelopment into a "world-class
OL,9,Fcountry club".
OL,11,FConstruction at the site previously
OL,12,Fcaused controversy and frustration
OL,13,Famongst locals when 30-metre-high
OL,14,Ftowers were built as part of the
OL,15,Fdevelopment.
OL,17,FWhen asked if there is anything
OL,18,FStephen wishes had gone differently
OL,19,Fabout the revamp, he explains: "I'd
OL,20,Fhave liked planning to be easier.
