OL,3,CBillionaire Guernsey golf investor
OL,4,Cwants to inspire tourism boost
OL,6,F"I would like the people to have had
OL,7,Fthe vision alongside me and not fight
OL,8,Fit. Listen to what we were saying and
OL,9,Fnot try and tell us what to do.
OL,11,F"But we fought through all that, we've
OL,12,Fgot here, and I think when it's all
OL,13,Ffinished, everybody will say, 'Well,
OL,14,Fhe was right'.
OL,16,F"The biggest compliment that was paid
OL,17,Fto me was the Lieutenant Governor told
OL,18,Fme, 'This looks like a golf course
OL,19,Finside a nature reserve'."
